<hw>IRA</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Finance)</fld> <def>individual
retirement account; -- a special type of savings account allowed by law
to provide deferred taxation of the interest paid.</def> <mark>[U.S.,
acronym]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> individual retirement account.</syn>⟦br⟧
