==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: IRA
<hw>IRA</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The Irish Republican Army, a group in
Ireland with the primary goal of promoting the unification of Ireland
and the severing of the political bond of Northern Ireland with Great
Britain, of mostly secret membership, with a militant wing sponsoring
terrorist activities such as bombings and the killings of police,
British soldiers, and Unionist sympathizers in Northern Ireland.</def>
<mark>[Acronym]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Iracund</ent>⟦br⟧
